            Cull Front
            ZWrite Off
            ZTest Greater
            // using alpha compositing https://developer.nvidia.com/gpugems/GPUGems3/gpugems3_ch23.html
			Blend 0 SrcAlpha OneMinusSrcAlpha, Zero OneMinusSrcAlpha
